ast.name: TV•remote
ast.comment:
App using JointSpace API to remote control Philips TV.

Wifi connection to TV required.

Should work with Philips
2k9 models (8000-9000 range, number ending with a 4) 2K10 models(7000-9000 range, number ending with a 5)
